snippet.title: Gunship Battle Total Warfare: Stars, fragments, and Dust. Complete Guide.
snippet.description:
Made a few star tutorial video's.
However they are outdated or non applicable at this point. With all the new content added I wanted to redo everything completely. For those who struggle with making stars. and some advice on mistakes I made wasting valuable rss and fragments.
